<p><span class="Dummytitle">Author's Post</span></p>
<div class="info"><span class="printuser avatarhover"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:only-once-away-my-son-5/decibelleaccount.png" class="small" alt="decibelleaccount.png" /><span class="fake-link">Decibelles</span></span> 20 Nov 2017, 10:09</div>
