<div class="dummyContent">
<p>I think I'll rest on what to fix from this and what not to fix. A lot of the surreal stuff (and some of the tone stuff you point out) is intentional, but eh, I'll wait and see. Right now it's at -2 so I might consider how much to retool. Thanks!</p>
</div>
